Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found a wish that I want fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to use this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! If you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been protected by Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of that, I'm still here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the answer that I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely will not waste all of Homura-chan's effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gathered the cause-and-effects of countless worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you manifest all of those, you can probably fulfill any wish you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kaname Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for your soul, what do you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.14,0:01:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that every Witch was erased before they were even born!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every Witch from the entire universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the Witches from the past and the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With these hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you realize this wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's greater in magnitude than tampering with time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a violation of the principle of cause-and-effect itself! {LOL HE GOT PWNED SO HARD}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really want to become a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God or whatever is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who has fought Witches up until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the Magical Girls who believed in hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to keep their smiles even to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those rules that hinder me from doing so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me break them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me change them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fulfill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incubator!
