Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname-san, do you understand how scary that wish is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you are beginning is an endless battle throughout time, in both the past and the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, you definitely will not be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't as simple as "death".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though the future is eternal, the concept of exterminating Witches will be corrected in this universe. {TLC: means she'll be able to fix this universe but for the futur that battle will be eternal}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. That's my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone else tells me that having hope is a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will reject that statement every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I would have to. {Consistency check with Ep11}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go try it, regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found a reason to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You decided not to run and hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only other option is to charge forward with all your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thank you, Kyoko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I have to return something that you had left with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not actually fulfilling your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are becoming hope itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming the hope of all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wishes will definitely not be allowed to end in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have to curse anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have to hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bear all the cause-and-effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hate anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to curse anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you become that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the new causal laws that Madoka brought, the universe is reworked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Magical Girl that can travel through time as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's go see the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The result of the existence of Kaname Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Soul Gem that her wish had created.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... {TLC/edit since I'm a timer :p}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The price to realize this oversized wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how heavy the burden that Madoka has to shoulder is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realizing a wish that is akin to creating a universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That also means enough despair to end a universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish was the destruction of all Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is really fulfilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I... do not need to despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, this way, your life loses its beginning and end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The evidence and memories of your life on Earth will cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence will become a higher plane and become a mere concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will be able to sense you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to interact with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are no longer a member of this universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the conclusion that Madoka had hoped for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she got in return in the end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What joke is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This outcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much! It's worse than death; it's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong, Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can now see all of time, both the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see all of past universes, regardless if they existed or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all of the new universes that may or may not come into existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I know all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In all the timelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effort that you put forth for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were so many times you cried, with your body injured all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even like that, you continued to fight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize it all this time, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I am the way I am now that I can truly understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think how great of a friend I really had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my greatest friend! {OK HOLD UP HOLD UP! WHAT THE FUCK HAPPENED TO SAYAKA? MADOKA IS SUCH A BITCH FOR CHANGING HER BFF SO FAST}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this way, you will lose a home to return to, and will be forced to leave everyone you loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll be all alone in this place forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not alone. {YOU SEE WHAT I DID THERE? DOH HO HO} {>NGE references}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is with me, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The me from now on will be omnipresent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't see or hear me, I'll always be right beside you, Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, is that what you really desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't remember you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to even feel Madoka anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able come to this place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, even if you go back to the original world, you will probably still remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Magical Girls can realize dreams and hopes! {I'M SENSING A NICE BOAT ENDING}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there's just a small chance, miracles may come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka! Don't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have to go welcome everyone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And though I can't say when, we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But until then, we'll have to separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 25, Kamijou Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The piece performed:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ave Maria. {LOL SERIOUSLY? THAT'S A KIDDIE PIECE!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To save you, I could only erase everything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, this future will disappear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this probably isn't how you wished for it to be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you worked so hard to fulfill your wish, I thought that it was really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It definitely couldn't be something meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I only wanted to listen to him perform again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped that more people could hear that violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all I can remember, then it's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing left to regret anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm a little envious, I can't help it if it's Hitomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a nice girl that's clearly good toward Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can definitely make him... happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Sayaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:16:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left, led by her circular logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki-san, that strike just now used up all of your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! What meaning is there if she disappears, even for the man she loves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. We finally became friends after so many difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the fate of a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have understood it when you received your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The result of pursuing hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before bringing curses to this world, we can only disappear like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka! Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can't do that, Tatsuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't pull on a girl's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka! Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was me. Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's the invisible friend that he sees when he plays alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This happens quite often among children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I remember it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:18:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, do you know that person, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a character from some anime or something? {LOL} {Yes, yes it is...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have heard it somewhere, but I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have met her with Tatsuya somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I really feel that this sounds familiar in my memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ribbon is really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It fits my tastes a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty surprised myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fit for an auntie like me~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if I had a daughter, maybe I'd let her tie it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you said can definitely be a valid hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's true, there's no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's like you said, and the laws of the universe have been rewritten,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have no possible way of verifying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're the only one who holds those memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you still can't distinguish reality from the fantasy that exists only in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did all of the Soul Gems that couldn't be purified disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't understood that phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding that, the concept of the Witches that appears in your story greatly interests me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Collecting the energy from human emotion is definitely a charming idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If such an elegant solution really existed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the tactics of us Incubators would probably be completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the world of Witches you talked about, there weren't any Magical Demons{???, original below} like those we fight now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this way of collecting curses exceptionally simpler?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our relationship with you{you for humans here} was also very treacherous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't understand the moral views of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in a world that will not give birth to Witches,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't mean that the curses of the world will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warping this world has merely changed its form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it is aiming at humans from a dark abyss. {Needs check}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight is truly a night filled with a thick atmosphere of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Magical Demons{???} are also appearing one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many we destroy, they keep coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Complaining won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though this world is filled with repeated sorrow and hatred, and isn't worth saving,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's still a place that she wanted to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I will continue...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be brave.
